   "source": [
    "# Actividad 1 – Dibujo de objetos 3D, visualización y proyección\n",
    "## Creeper de Minecraft con PyOpenGL\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Importaciones y constantes de color\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from OpenGL.GL   import *\n",
    "from OpenGL.GLU  import *\n",
    "from OpenGL.GLUT import *\n",
    "import math, sys\n",
    "\n",
    "# Paleta de colores del Creeper\n",
    "GREEN_LIGHT  = (0.18, 0.70, 0.18)   # verde claro cuerpo\n",
    "GREEN_DARK   = (0.08, 0.42, 0.08)   # verde oscuro detalle\n",
    "BLACK_FACE   = (0.05, 0.05, 0.05)   # negro cara\n",
    "GREEN_MID    = (0.12, 0.55, 0.12)   # verde medio pies/cuerpo\n",
    "\n",
    "WIN_W, WIN_H = 1000, 800\n",
    "cam_angle_x = 20.0\n",
    "cam_angle_y = -40.0\n",
    "cam_zoom    = 40.0\n",
    "last_x = last_y = 0\n",
    "mouse_btn = None"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Primitiva: cubo unitario (`color_cube`)\n",
    "\n",
    "Dibuja un cubo de lado 1 centrado en el origen con todas las caras del mismo color (enunciado).\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def color_cube(colorv):
    """
    Función que dibuja un cubo centrado en el origen y de lado 1
    con todas las caras del color pasado por parámetro a la función.
    El color se pasa en una lista de tres componentes.
    """
  "  he = 0.5   # semilado del cubo (half-edge)

  "  v1 = [-he, -he,  he]
  "  v2 = [-he,  he,  he]
   " v3 = [ he, -he,  he]
    "v4 = [ he,  he,  he]
    "v5 = [ he, -he, -he]
    "v6 = [ he,  he, -he]
    "v7 = [-he,  he, -he]
    "v8 = [-he, -he, -he]

    "glColor3fv(colorv)

    "# CARA POSTERIOR
    "glBegin(GL_POLYGON)
    "glVertex3fv(v8)
    "glVertex3fv(v7)
    "glVertex3fv(v6)
    "glVertex3fv(v5)
    "glEnd()

   " # CARA FRONTAL
    "glBegin(GL_POLYGON)
    "glVertex3fv(v1)
    "glVertex3fv(v3)
    "glVertex3fv(v4)
    "glVertex3fv(v2)
    "glEnd()

  "  # CARA DERECHA
    "glBegin(GL_POLYGON)
    "glVertex3fv(v3)
    "glVertex3fv(v5)
    "glVertex3fv(v6)
    "glVertex3fv(v4)
    "glEnd()

    "# CARA IZQUIERDA
    "glBegin(GL_POLYGON)
    "glVertex3fv(v1)
    "glVertex3fv(v2)
    "glVertex3fv(v7)
    "glVertex3fv(v8)
    "glEnd()

    "# CARA INFERIOR
    "glBegin(GL_POLYGON)
    "glVertex3fv(v1)
    "glVertex3fv(v3)
    "glVertex3fv(v5)
    "glVertex3fv(v8)
    "glEnd()

   " # CARA SUPERIOR
    "glBegin(GL_POLYGON)
    "glVertex3fv(v2)
    "glVertex3fv(v4)
    "glVertex3fv(v6)
    "glVertex3fv(v7)
    "glEnd()
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Función auxiliar\n",
    "\n",
    "Permite construir cualquier bloque rectangular de cubos unitarios."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def draw_orthohedron(cx, cy, cz, W, D, H, color, hollow=True):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    Bloque W×D×H de cubos unitarios centrado en (cx, cy, cz).\n",
    "    hollow=True → sólo capa exterior (elementos huecos).\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    ox = cx - W/2.0 + 0.5\n",
    "    oy = cy - H/2.0 + 0.5\n",
    "    oz = cz - D/2.0 + 0.5\n",
    "    for ix in range(W):\n",
    "        for iy in range(H):\n",
    "            for iz in range(D):\n",
    "                if hollow:\n",
    "                    if not (ix==0 or ix==W-1 or iy==0 or iy==H-1 or iz==0 or iz==D-1):\n",
    "                        continue\n",
    "                glPushMatrix()\n",
    "                glTranslatef(ox+ix, oy+iy, oz+iz)\n",
    "                color_cube(color)\n",
    "                glPopMatrix()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Cara del Creeper\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def draw_face(head_cx, head_cy, head_cz, head_H):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Dibuja ojos y boca negros sobre la cara frontal de la cabeza.\"\"\"\n",
    "    z_face = head_cz + 4.0 + 0.01\n",
    "    eye_positions = [\n",
    "        (-2, head_cy+1.5), (-1, head_cy+1.5),\n",
    "        (-2, head_cy+0.5), (-1, head_cy+0.5),\n",
    "        ( 1, head_cy+1.5), ( 2, head_cy+1.5),\n",
    "        ( 1, head_cy+0.5), ( 2, head_cy+0.5),\n",
    "    ]\n",
    "    mouth_positions = [\n",
    "        (-1, head_cy-0.5),(0, head_cy-0.5),(1, head_cy-0.5),\n",
    "        (-2, head_cy-1.5),(-1, head_cy-1.5),(0, head_cy-1.5),(1, head_cy-1.5),(2, head_cy-1.5),\n",
    "        (-1, head_cy-2.5),(0, head_cy-2.5),(1, head_cy-2.5),\n",
    "    ]\n",
    "    for (x, y) in eye_positions + mouth_positions:\n",
    "        glPushMatrix()\n",
    "        glTranslatef(head_cx+x, y, z_face)\n",
    "        glScalef(1.0, 1.0, 0.02)\n",
    "        color_cube(BLACK_FACE)\n",
    "        glPopMatrix()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Ensamblaje del Creeper\n",
    "| Elemento | Ancho X | Fondo Z | Alto Y | Centro Y | Notas |\n",
    "|----------|---------|---------|--------|----------|-------|\n",
    "| Pie izq  | 8 | 4 | 6 | 3  | CentroX = -5 |\n",
    "| Pie der  | 8 | 4 | 6 | 3  | CentroX = +5 |\n",
    "| Cuerpo   | 8 | 4 | 12 | 11 | Solapa 1 cubo con pies |\n",
    "| Cabeza   | 8 | 8 | 8 | 21 | Centrada con cuerpo |\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def draw_creeper():\n",
    "    \"\"\"Ensambla el Creeper completo.\"\"\"\n",
    "    # Pies\n",
    "    draw_orthohedron(-5, 3.0, 0.0, 8, 4, 6, GREEN_MID,   hollow=True)\n",
    "    draw_orthohedron(+5, 3.0, 0.0, 8, 4, 6, GREEN_DARK,  hollow=True)\n",
    "    # Cuerpo (base en Y=5 → solapamiento de 1 cubo con pies)\n",
    "    draw_orthohedron(0, 11.0, 0.0, 8, 4, 12, GREEN_LIGHT, hollow=True)\n",
    "    # Cabeza (sobre el cuerpo, centrada)\n",
    "    draw_orthohedron(0, 21.0, 0.0, 8, 8,  8, GREEN_LIGHT, hollow=True)\n",
    "    # Cara\n",
    "    draw_face(0, 21.0, 0.0, 8)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. Proyecciones\n",
    "\n",
    "Se implementan tres tipos de proyección: - Ortográfica, Perspectiva cónica y Oblicua"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def set_ortho_projection(W, H, extent=30):\n",
    "    ratio = W/H if H>0 else 1\n",
    "    glMatrixMode(GL_PROJECTION); glLoadIdentity()\n",
    "    glOrtho(-extent*ratio, extent*ratio, -extent, extent, -200, 200)\n",
    "    glMatrixMode(GL_MODELVIEW)\n",
    "\n",
    "def set_perspective_projection(W, H):\n",
    "    glMatrixMode(GL_PROJECTION); glLoadIdentity()\n",
    "    gluPerspective(45.0, W/H if H>0 else 1, 0.1, 500.0)\n",
    "    glMatrixMode(GL_MODELVIEW)\n",
    "\n",
    "def set_oblique_cabinet_projection(W, H, extent=30):\n",
    "    ratio = W/H if H>0 else 1\n",
    "    glMatrixMode(GL_PROJECTION); glLoadIdentity()\n",
    "    glOrtho(-extent*ratio, extent*ratio, -extent, extent, -200, 200)\n",
    "    f, a = 0.5, math.radians(45)\n",
    "    shear = [1,0,0,0, 0,1,0,0, -f*math.cos(a),-f*math.sin(a),1,0, 0,0,0,1]\n",
    "    glMultMatrixf(shear)\n",
    "    glMatrixMode(GL_MODELVIEW)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. Uso de GLUT\n",
